: 381}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Blitzboks, under the guidance of coach Philip Snyman and captain Selvyn Davids, will fly out of South Africa for France on Wednesday night, hoping to find a pot of gold at the end of what has been a poor year which almost saw the team miss out on the Olympics.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philip Snyman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\"}, {\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selvyn_Davids\", \"score\": 0.9999999999217835, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Selvyn Davids\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selvyn_Davids\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selvyn_Davids\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5128291076552882e-14, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999995175131, \"rank\": 4.824778330393495e-10, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Blitzboks\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"the guidance\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from