"from\": 917, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"all 11 other challengers\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"their spot\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now there is again hope that the Blitzboks can pull off something special in Paris.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999997149871, \"rank\": 2.8500507779754426e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"the Blitzboks\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot has changed and all for the good,\\\" said former captain and one of the team's most senior players, Siviwe Soyizwapi, on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siviwe_Soyizwapi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Siviwe Soyizwapi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siviwe_Soyizwapi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siviwe_Soyizwapi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"the good\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"former captain\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"the team's most senior players\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are going to France knowing that we back ourselves to get a result.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999995175131, \"rank\": 4.824778330393495e-10, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We worked incredibly hard to put ourselves back into the race for a medal.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me personally, the knowledge that my body is back to full strength (after a long injury layoff) and that my teammates are fit and ready make this an exciting trip.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the knowledge\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"full strength\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"a long injury layoff\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We know what we know, to use a well-known phrase.\\\"\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a well-known phrase\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old wing will be going to his second Olympic Games, but few would argue that the first one, in Tokyo in 2021, was a memorable one.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9964419262326614, \"rank\": 0.0035706735293612956, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}